    "en": {
      "title": "Grace period for vehicle revenue licenses",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st);\u00a0A grace period has been granted for vehicles registered in the Western Province to obtain vehicle revenue licenses.",
        "A statement issued by the Chief Secretary of the Western Province, Jayanthi Wijetunga states that a grace period will be given until the 29th of July.",
        "The statement adds that no fines will be levied during the relevant grace period."
      ],
